item.description: Terminal Terminal is a recreation of a classic map from the game Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2. The layout of this recreation shares many similarities with the original, however, utilizes a different art style. Los Pollos Los Pollos is a recreation of the iconic fast food chain from the hit tv show Breaking Bad. North Peak North Peak is a small town located in a snow covered valley.
